a) The Universities

ARTICLE 120 - Universities shall be established only by State and by legis-
lation. The Universities are public corporate bodies enjoying academic and adminis-
trative autonomy.

Universities shall be administered and supervised by _ organs. consisting of
qualified members of the teaching staff elected from among themselves. The provi}
sions governing State Universities established by special laws are reserved."
